h. Publication date 1st October 2013.","feed":null,"feeds":null,"favicon":"http://www.bbc.co.uk/favicon.ico","description":"The extraordinary life of Lord Castlereagh (1769 - 1822), one of the most successful and most hated politicians of his day","datetime":"2013-10-01 12:00:00 +0100"}
